      <p class="max-w-md mt-6 text-base text-gray-300 sm:text-lg md:mt-6 md:max-w-3xl">
        Bonfire is made of lots of moving parts - called <a href="/extensions"><b>extensions</b></a> - tied together by shared user identities and activity feeds, which can be configured in great detail so they behave and look just right for you. 
      <p class="max-w-md mt-6 text-base text-gray-300 sm:text-lg md:mt-6 md:max-w-3xl">Designers and developers can also "fork" extensions to further customise them or create new ones. Users can choose which ones to install and even ask the ecosystem for specific features or changes - based on their unique values, needs, and preferences. 

      <p class="max-w-md mt-6 text-base text-gray-300 sm:text-lg md:mt-6 md:max-w-3xl">
